              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "PRJFS"
                ],
                "institute": "3CPRIMP"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The Radioactive Ion Beam Line in",
                "Lanzhou (RIBLL)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 13C primary beam was accelerated to 50 MeV/u by",
                "HIRFL. The natural Be target (2000 um thick) was",
                "bombarded, and then 6He was produced with 25 MeV/u by",
                "the projectile fragmentation process of 13C+Be,",
                "separated and purified by the Radioactive Ion Beam",
                "Line in Lanzhou (RIBLL)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The secondary Be target was 200 um 9Be."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two 200 um plastic scintillation detectors",
                "were used to measure the time of flight (TOF) and the",
                "energy loss delta E."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MWPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two low pressure multi-wire proportional",
                "counters (LPMWPC) were used to measure the direction",
                "and location of incident beam, installed before the",
                "target."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "PS",
                "SI",
                "CSICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The reaction products were",
                "detected and identified by six telescope systems.",
                "Every one consisted of a position sensitive silicon",
                "detector (thickness with 320 um, effective area with",
                "45x45 mm2), a large area silicon detector (thickness",
                "with 250 um, diameter with 45 mm) and a CsI",
                " (Tl) scintillation detector (thickness with 250 um,",
                "diameter with 45 mm)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF",
                "EDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
